              FULL REBUILD
            </h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 13px;">
              Complete system overhaul — new motherboard, CPU, RAM, and SSD. Keep your case and
              peripherals while getting a modern, fast system at a lower cost than buying new.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0;">
