              Yes! Most laptops can have their SSD and RAM upgraded. Some newer ultra-thin models
              have soldered components, but we'll check compatibility before quoting. We upgrade
              all major brands including Dell, HP, Lenovo, Asus, and Acer.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3
              class="space-font"
              style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;"
            >
              How long does a computer upgrade take?
            </h3>
