              Most upgrades are completed same day or within 24 hours. SSD cloning can take a few
              hours depending on the amount of data. We're open 7 days, 9AM-9PM, and offer
              collection and drop-off service throughout Romford.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

